    "description": "The computational model must satisfy FDA guidance on computational fluid dynamics modeling for cardiovascular devices (2016) and ASME V&V 40-2018 credibility requirements at Model Risk Level 2. Acceptance criterion: relative hemolysis index RH < 1.0 across all 5 operating points; all assessed credibility factors must meet or exceed required gradation levels.",
    "source": "https://doi.org/10.1115/1.4035672"
