    "outcome": "Accepted",
    "rationale": "All 7 assessed credibility factors meet or exceed required gradation levels for MRL 2. Six factors appropriately scoped out per ASME V&V 40 Table 3 for Medium model influence and High decision consequence at MRL 2. Validation metric (MARE 8.3%) satisfies MRL 2 threshold. Mesh convergence GCI < 2% confirms discretization error is adequately controlled. The CFD model is assessed as credible for identifying worst-case hemolysis operating conditions for the Class II CPB device. Decision: Accepted.",
